Backcountry camping (registration) for Paradise Meadows and certain regions of Forbidden Plateau. The main access route to Forbidden Plateau from Courtenay and Campbell River is via the Paradise Meadows trailhead at Mount Washington. From Highway 19 follow signs to Mount Washington ski resort via exit #130 (the Strathcona Parkway) for 20km. Turn left onto the Nordic Lodge road for 1.5km to the Paradise Meadows parking lot. Lake Helen Mackenzie, Kwai Lake, and Circlet Lake campgrounds are accessed from the Paradise Meadows trailhead. Most sites offer pit toilets and food caches. Circlet Lake 20 sites, Lake Helen Mackenzie 10 sites, Kwai Lake 15 sites. FCFS.
